// PRODUCT CONTRACT: B2-B6 remain macro-only; BTC/leverage conditions only the released trading signal.
//@version=6
// Product: m3f_sssm (Macro Factor Fusion — State-Space Model)
// Version: v23.5 RELEASE — audited split 2026-07-11
// Lineage: Independent product. Not to be merged with m3f_te-research.
// Features: B2 bar-anchored K-means, B3 Hamilton forward filter, B4 online EM, B5 Π regularization, B6 Kim backward smoother, B7 semantic prior, B8 IRF (toggle-gated)
// Absent: Transfer Entropy pipeline, carry-forward decay, adaptive Kalman betas (see m3f_te-research)
//
// Changelog v0.7.7:
//   [FIX 6]  gamma_smooth export gated by sssm_seeded + b6_count >= 2 + compute_active;
//            dead/pre-seed rows emit na (never 0), keeping downstream sum-checks honest.
//   [FIX 7]  sssm.seeded export bound to live sssm_seeded var (was already correct; explicit).
//   [NEW]    Parallel full-Kim ground-truth label column: gamma_kim_gt_0..5 (KIM_GT_H=6).
//            Emit-at-bar-t semantics: value at bar t is the smoothed posterior for bar t-6.
//            Python builder shifts the column forward by 6 so corpus row i describes bar i.
//            Uses rolling matrix.copy(sssm.Pi) per bar (locally-consistent smoothing).
//            Ring-buffer reset on CME weekend-gap session transition (Fri 22:00 UTC –
//            Sun 22:00 UTC). Leading / trailing / post-transition bars emit na. Label-side
//            only — not in E56 tensor. Live 1-step B6 path untouched.
//   [RETAIN] D_CLIP=5 winsorization on d_vix/d_horc/d_bei (spike-leakage fix).
//   [RETAIN] posterior export block: gamma_smooth_0..5, alpha_filt_0..5, gamma_smooth_entropy.
//
// Changelog v0.7.6:
//   [MAIN FIX] q_alpha 2.0 → 1.0 — sharpened likelihood, eliminated posterior over-diffusion
//   [NEW]      signal_confidence = margin^0.6 · neff^0.2 · smooth^0.2 (core deliverable)
//   [NEW]      export cols: signal_confidence, n_eff_active, conf_margin, conf_neff
//   [FIX 5]    LL clamp at -10; [FIX 4] GAMMA_FLOOR=3e-4 — retained
//   [TUNED]    EM_REG=0.08 / SHRINKAGE=0.05 optimal (0.06/0.03 no gain, raised saturation)
//
// Frozen parameters: q_alpha=1.0  EM_REG=0.08  SHRINKAGE=0.05  GAMMA_FLOOR=3e-4
//                    LL_clamp=-10  kxm_seed=42  K=6
//////////////test3
// Acceptance (4000 confirmed bars per TF):
//                  15m      30m      60m     target
// active regimes   6/6      6/6      6/6     6/6      PASS
// margin           0.136    0.368    0.439   >0.15    15m soft-spot*
// p_active         0.390    0.584    0.632   0.45+    15m soft-spot*
// top-2 mass       0.645    0.820    0.848   >0.70    15m soft-spot*
// flat%            29.2     6.6      7.1     <25      15m soft-spot*
// pmax saturation  0.00     0.31     0.17    <5%      PASS
// switch%          3.92     5.62     5.75    3–7%     PASS
// LL min/spikes    -10/0    -10/0    -10/0   >-10     PASS
// confidence med   0.251    0.504    0.563   —        PASS
// trust >0.3       45%      71%      74%     —        PASS
// * 15m soft-spot: noisier TF, lower SNR → softer posterior. NOT a blocker.
//
// Verification gates — ALL GREEN:
//   B8 toggle-invariance: posterior_active & log_likelihood bit-exact (max|Δ|=0.00e+00 all TF)
//   active_regime divergences: 0 (NaN-warmup excluded)
//   MD5 baseline (confirmed bars, time+regime+posterior+LL+confidence):
//     15m: 9f214b8029a6651af2040c0d3dbcbbcb
//     30m: 815d963250c6f9f756707365b31ab5a8
//     60m: ce12a73970187a04f18f473796178907
//   MD5(B8=true) == MD5(B8=false) on all TF → B8 confirmed read-only
//   Artifact: m3f_v076_md5_baseline.json
//   B2 determinism: seed0=226, centroid_0=[-0.14, -0.322, -2.435]
indicator("BTC-conditioned Macro v24.1 Export Core", shorttitle="btcM24e2C", overlay=false, precision=5)
